      "answer": "服务启动步骤的第2步是：执行 `docker compose up --build -d`。",
      "topItems": [
        {
          "title": "Orion Ops Runbook",
          "heading": "服务启动步骤",
          "sectionPath": "Orion 运行手册 > 服务启动步骤",
          "chunkType": "section",
          "sourceType": "md",
          "text": "[Heading] 服务启动步骤\n\n1. 检查 .env 配置。\n2. 执行 docker compose up --build -d。\n3. 访问 /health 确认 gateway 和 ai-service 可用。"
        },
        {
          "title": "Orion Ops Runbook",
          "heading": "初步排查",
          "sectionPath": "Orion 运行手册 > 初步排查",
          "chunkType": "section",
          "sourceType": "md",
          "text": "[Heading] 初步排查\n\n1. 先看 gateway 健康状态。\n2. 再检查 ai-service 日志。\n3. 最后确认 PostgreSQL 和 Redis 连接。"
        },
        {
          "title": "Orion Ops Runbook",
          "heading": "升级规则",
          "sectionPath": "Orion 运行手册 > 升级规则",
          "chunkType": "section",
          "sourceType": "md",
          "text": "[Heading] 升级规则\n\n如果十五分钟内无法恢复，就升级给值班负责人和后端负责人。"
        }
      ],
